name: HackQuest
fullText:
Introducing the Monthly Builder’s Trial 🐉
Our new monthly hackathon!

Each month, the Quack State proclaims a Trial.
Builders create, and one ascends as The Chosen One 👑

Not prize-focused, but spotlight-focused ⚡
Projects get the traction and recognition they deserve. https://t.co/fq5tTygXX3
